cc:Work.dc:description: Geoff Ritter's personal logo design diagram

g.aria-label: Geoff Ritter's personal logo containing a squared G with rounded corners and an intertwined reversed R on a square background with rounded corners. At the bottom is a bar containing, in all capital letters, the words GEOFF RITTER.
Black and white variant of the logo. There is no background, the R is outlined, and the bar at the bottom is fully rounded on both sides.

path.aria-label: pointing to background of the logo.
The color dark red in hexadecimal #B40000
pointing to the G in the middle of the logo
The color pure black in hexadecimal #000000
pointing to the reversed R in the middle of the logo
The color pure white in hexadecimal #FFFFFF

g.aria-label: describing the uniformity of the logo

path.aria-label: The logo is square and divided into eighths both vertically and horizontally
The logo was designed to be 256 units wide by 256 units tall
A one eighth marker showing that the G and R are both five eigths wide and tall with a line thickness of one eighth and are evenly spaced within the logo.
Each division in this design is 32 units.
One third of a division pointing to left side of the G in the bar.
One third of a division pointing to right side of R in the bar
pointing to rounded corners in logo
All corners are the same; 10% the length of the G. In this design, 16 unit rounding
pointing to text in logo
"Geoff Ritter" text is Montserrat and should not appear when logo is smaller than 160px on screen or 1 inch in print.
Pointing to the bar at the bottom of the logo
Bar should not appear when logo is smaller than 65 pixels on screen or 0.5 inches in print.
pointing to space next to the logo
Spacing around logo should equal the one eighth division of the logo
pointing to the leg of the R
The leg of the R is at 45 degrees.
If floating above the bar, it comes to a point.
The rounding node starts at exactly two eighths left and one eighth up
The bottom edge touches the midpoint of the inside arc
Black and white variant must:
Have full rounding on bar
No outline on the logo
Outside stroke on the R that is one thirty second the width of the logo. In this design, 8 units thick.
